Proverbs 16-31 <t><f>ⓦ</f> Gray hair is <f>ⓧ</f>a crown of glory; </t><t>it <f>ⓨ</f>is gained in a righteous life.</t>
Proverbs 16-32 <t><f>ⓩ</f> Whoever is slow to anger is better than the mighty, </t><t>and he who rules his spirit than he who takes a city.</t>
